## ABOUT THE AUTHOR (2,400 char max)

```html
<p><b>{AUTHOR NAME}</b> is a {one-line credibility headline}.</p>

<p>{Two-sentence biography of past credentials, books, work.}</p>

<p>{Two sentences of relevant personal detail — where they live,
family, what their writing comes out of.}</p>

<p><i>{TITLE}</i> is {their first novel / their Nth book in the X
series / their debut in a new genre}.</p>
```

---

## FROM THE AUTHOR (optional — 4,000 char field)

A personal note from the author. 1,000-2,000 chars. Conversational
register. Should sound like a letter to the reader, not a marketing
blurb.

```html
<p>{Personal opening — why this book, why now, what life-event or
fascination got it started.}</p>

<p>{Middle — what it was like writing this, what surprised you,
what you hope a reader takes away.}</p>

<p>{Close — invite the reader in. "If you've ever stayed up past
midnight because you 'just had to finish one more chapter' — welcome
home."}</p>
```

