## 7 KEYWORDS (KDP backend search terms)

Keep each <= 50 chars. Don't repeat the title or author name (KDP indexes
those automatically). Mix one-word terms and three-word phrases.

1. `{keyword 1}`
2. `{keyword 2}`
3. `{keyword 3}`
4. `{keyword 4}`
5. `{keyword 5}`
6. `{keyword 6}`
7. `{keyword 7}`

