## 2 BISAC CATEGORIES

KDP lets you choose 2 BISAC subject codes plus 10 (paid) browse-path
categories.

- Primary BISAC: `{CODE — e.g., FIC031000 = Fiction / Thrillers / General}`
- Secondary BISAC: `{CODE — e.g., FIC042000 = Fiction / Christian / Suspense}`

Recommended browse paths (request via KDP support):
- Books › {category path}
- Kindle eBooks › {category path}

