## PRICING (your call — these are common patterns)

| Format | Price | Royalty |
|--------|-------|---------|
| Kindle eBook | $4.99 - $6.99 | 70% (USD $2.99-$9.99 range) |
| Paperback | $12.99 - $17.99 | 60% minus printing cost |
| Hardcover | $24.99 - $29.99 | 60% minus printing cost |

KDP shows you the actual royalty before you publish. Color paperback
interior multiplies your printing cost ~3x — keep cover-paper / B&W
interior for thrillers and most fiction to keep the price reasonable.

---

## A+ CONTENT MODULES (KDP Author Central)

A+ Content is the rich-media area below the listing. KDP allows up to
7 modules. Suggested modules:

1. Hero banner with cover + tagline
2. "From the back cover" three-paragraph block with chapter art
3. About-the-author photo + bio paragraph
4. "If you loved X" comp-title grid
5. Newsletter signup CTA (link to your subscriber landing page)
6. Map / artifact image with caption (if your book has one)
7. Series tease (only after book 2 announced)
